flowchart TD
    A[Start: alma_multiply] --> B{n <= 256?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Single BLAS dgemm]
    B -->|No| D[Allocate metadata arrays]
    D --> E[Classify all blocks]
    E --> F[Initialize C to zero]
    F --> G[Parallel block multiply]
    G --> H[For each block pair]
    H --> I[dgemm accumulation]
    I --> J[Free metadata]
    J --> K[End]
    C --> K
